# Native std.http Response provider

[Response, cacheable, noCache](std/http.ssc)

```scalascript
val text = Response.text("hello", 201)
println(text.status)
println(text.headers("Content-Type"))
println(text.body)
val json = Response.json(Map("ok" -> true, "n" -> 2))
println(json.body)
val cached = cacheable(text, 60, "v1")
println(cached.headers("Cache-Control"))
println(cached.headers("ETag"))
println(noCache(text).headers("Cache-Control"))
```
